%F A217975 a(n) = 6*a(n - 2) - a(n - 4) with a(1)=2, a(2)=4, a(3)=8, a(4)=22. - _Sture Sjöstedt_, Oct 16 2012
%F A217975 a(n)*a(n+3)-a(n+1)*a(n+2) = 10-2*(-1)^n. - _Bruno Berselli_, Oct 25 2012
