%F A217975 a(n) = a(-n+1) = ((4+sqrt(2))*(1-(-1)^n*sqrt(2))^(2*floor(n/2))+(4-sqrt(2))*(1+(-1)^n*sqrt(2))^(2*floor(n/2)))/4. - _Bruno Berselli_, Oct 25 2012
%F A217975 a(2n-1) = A078343(2n-1), a(2n) = A100525(n-1). - _Bruno Berselli_, Oct 25 2012
